---
// src/pages/privacy-policy.astro
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
const updated = 'March 2025';
---
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy for Deskbly.com" />
    <style>
      .page { max-width: 720px; margin: 3rem auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }
      h1 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: #111; }
      h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-top: 2rem; }
      p, li { line-height: 1.8; color: #444; }
      ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
      .updated { color: #999; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main class="page">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: {updated}</p>

      <p>Deskbly ("we", "us", or "our") operates deskbly.com. This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data when you use our site.</p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We may collect non-personally identifiable information such as browser type, pages visited, and time spent on the site through analytics tools (e.g. Google Analytics).</p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use cookies to improve your experience on our site. Cookies are small files stored on your device. Third-party services such as Google AdSense may also place cookies on your device for advertising purposes. You can instruct your browser to refuse all cookies or indicate when a cookie is being sent.</p>

      <h2>Google AdSense & Advertising</h2>
      <p>We use Google AdSense to display advertisements. Google may use cookies to serve ads based on your prior visits to our site or other sites. You can opt out of personalised advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ad Settings</a>.</p>

      <h2>Affiliate Links</h2>
      <p>Some links on this site are affiliate links. Clicking these links and making a purchase may result in us receiving a commission. We only recommend products we believe in. See our <a href="/disclaimer/">Disclaimer</a> for more details.</p>

      <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p>Our site may contain links to external websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of those sites.</p>

      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>Our site is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children.</p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this policy, please <a href="/contact/">contact us</a>.</p>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
